	--- mb rule
		--- < k > [putInMem(bitloc(Block:Nat, Base:Nat, Offset:Nat), tv(N:Int, T:Type), T:Type, tv(sNat(Len:Nat), J:Type))
		--- => putBitInMem(bitloc(Block:Nat, Base:Nat, Offset:Nat), ((N:Int %Int 2) +Int 2) %Int 2) ~> 
